query:
SELECT vs.id, vs.shopNumber, vs.mapMarkerX, vs.mapMarkerY
FROM vacant_shops vs
JOIN shopping_centres c ON vs.centreId = c.id
WHERE c.name = 'Eastgate Bondi Junction';
